<html>
<head>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container" style="margin: 0 auto;max-width: 600px;">
    <div class="belong-logo" style="text-align: center;margin: 5px;">
      <img alt="Belong" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RahulKondi/belongemail/master/img/belong.png" style="width:144px; height:54px;">
    </div>
    <div class="hero" style="background: #ff7f2a;padding: 15px 50px;text-align: left;max-width: 600px;font-size: 1.5em;color: white;margin: 0 auto;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: 2px 2px 2.5px #e6e6e6;text-shadow: 2px 2px #e42c5;">
      <p><b>Psychic experts believe that if someone misses you,
        you actually get to know that you're being missed.</b></p>
        <p>This email is how you know.</p>
      </div>
      {{#each rooms}}
      <div class="mention" style="font-size: 1.5em;color: #4d4d4d;margin-top: 50px;margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <b>{{this.textcreator}}</b> mentioned you in a discussion on Belong.
      </div>

      <div class="discussion-card" style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;border-radius: 5px;">
        <table class="discussion-section inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;margin: auto;max-width: 540px;padding: 25px;background-color: #fff;">
          <tr>
            <td>
              <div class="discussion-title" style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.25em;">
                {{this.tname}}
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              {{#if this.photo}}
              <div style="height: 200px; width: 500px; background-image: url({{this.photo}}); background-repeat: no-repeat"></div>
              {{/if}}
              {{#unless this.photo}}
              <div class="discussion-summary" style="color: #444444;margin-top: 10px;font-size: 1.25em;">
                {{this.tbody}}
              </div>
              {{/unless}}
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <span class="discussion-stamps inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;margin-top: 25px;color: #888888;font-size: 1em;">

                <span class="inline-blocks discussion-stamps-nickname" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;margin-right: 10px;">
                  <span class="inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;"> <img class="discussion-stamps-avatar" src="/i/picture?user={{this.threadcreator}}" alt="â‡£" style="border-radius: 50%;width: 24px;height: 24px;margin-right: 3px;"> </span>
                  <span class="inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;"> <b>{{this.threadcreator}}</b> </span>
                </span>
                <span class="inline-blocks discussion-stamps-location" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;margin-right: 10px;">
                  <span class="inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;">
                    <img class="discussion-stamps-location-pin" src="http://s.bel.ng/s/location.png" style="margin-right: 3px;">
                  </span>
                  <span class="inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;">
                  {{this.rname}}
                  </span>
                </span>
                {{#if this.upvote}}
                <span class="inline-blocks discussion-stamps-likes" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;">
                  <span class="inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;">
                    <img class="discussion-stamps-likes-heart" src="http://s.bel.ng/s/heart.png" style="width: 16px;height: 14.170px;">
                  </span>
                  <span class="inline-blocks" style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;">
                    {{this.upvote}} Likes
                  </span>
                </span>
                {{/if}}
              </span>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <table class="replies-section" style="margin: 25px auto auto 5px;max-width: 540px;min-width: 100%;">
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2">
            <div class="responses" style="font-weight: bold;color: #bbbbbb;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 25px;">
              Replies to this Discussion
            </div>
          </td>
          </tr><tr>
            </tr><tr>
              <td style="vertical-align: top;">
                <!--/i/picture?user={{this.textcreator}}-->
                <img class="replies-avatar" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ed/Nyan_cat_250px_frame.PNG/220px-Nyan_cat_250px_frame.PNG" alt="" style="border-radius: 50%;width: 48px;height: 48px;margin: auto; margin-top: 10px;">
              </td>
              <td style="width: 85%">
                <div class="replies-comment-box" style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;border-radius: 5px;padding: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;background-color: #f6f6f6; width: 510px">
                  <div class="replies-nickname" style="font-weight: bold;color: #666666;font-size: 1.25em;">{{this.textcreator}}</div>
                  <div class="replies-message" style="color: #444;margin-top: 10px;font-size: 1.25em;">
                    {{this.textbody}}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <div align="right" class="reply" style="margin: 25px auto;align: right;">
            <a class="reply-button" href="{{../this.domain}}/{{this.rid}}/{{this.tid}}{{this.utm}}" style="text-decoration: none;background: #ff1144;border-radius: 3px;box-shadow: 2px 2px 2.5px #e6e6e6;text-shadow: 2px 2px #e42c5;padding: 10px;text-align: center;font-size: 1.2em;font-weight: bold;max-width:80px;
  color: white;display: block;appearance: none;-webkit-appearance: none;-moz-appearance: none;border: 0;vertical-align: middle;">
              Reply
            </a>
          </div>
          {{/each}}
          <table class="footer" style="border-top: 1px solid #4d4d4d;margin-top: 50px;padding-top: 10px;font-size: 0.85em;color: #4d4d4d;">
            <tr>
              <td colspan="2">
                <b>&copy; Belong</b>  Your friendly neighborhood, #43, KR Garden, Murugeshpalya, Bangalore, Karnataka, 560017
                <p>Ignorance is bliss? <a href="{{domain}}/r/unsubscribe?email={{token}}" style="color:#6644bb; text-decoration: none"> Unsubscribe</a> </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
</div></body></html>
